sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Click remove member
    Frontend->>API: DELETE /api/workspaces/{id}/members/{userId}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace and target user
    DB-->>API: Workspace and user found

    alt Target is workspace owner
        API-->>Frontend: 400 Bad Request
        Frontend-->>Owner: Show protected-owner error
    else Removable member
        API->>DB: Remove membership
        DB-->>API: Membership deleted
        API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
        Frontend-->>Owner: Refresh members list
    end
